learning_outcomes.en:
A student who has completed the module:
is able to plan and conduct both scientific and applied research;
can assess the relevance of a research problem and choose a research topic;
can formulate research objectives, tasks and hypothesis;
knows how to plan a study in clinical pharmacy;
able to conduct research in accordance with ethical requirements;
can search for, systematize and analyze relevant scientific literature and synthesize and generalize the theoretical positions and research results presented therein (critical thinking);
can collect data and analyze their quality;
can choose a data analysis method, analyze research data and interpret the obtained results;
can present research results according to academic requirements.

learning_outcomes.et:
Mooduli läbinud üliõpilane:
hindab uurimisprobleemi aktuaalsust ja oskab valida teadusteemat;
oskab sõnastada uurimiseesmärke,  ülesandeid ja hüpoteesi;
kavandab kliinilise farmaatsia alase uurimuse;
viib läbi uuringut kooskõlas eetika nõuetega;
otsib, valib, süstematiseerib, analüüsib teemakohast teaduskirjandust ning sünteesib ja üldistab selles esitatud teoreetilisi seisukohti ning uurimistulemusi;
kriitiline mõtlemine.
